  "description": "Unofficial add-on for Whimscape & Armor Chroma.",
  "body": "## About\n> This is my attempt at applying the [<u>**Whimscape**</u>](https://modrinth.com/project/4YkvO5Rp) theme onto the [<u>**Armor Chroma**</u>](https://modrinth.com/project/pJnbPs9G) icons since I use them both in almost every minecraft instance I play.\n\n<p align=\"center\">\n  <img src=\"https://cdn.modrinth.com/data/cached_images/26683e61741ef3e0d6f7c2e60c4a47483bbc70f9.png\" alt=\"In game preview of the addon.\"/>\n</p>\n\n## Related Projects\n> Technically some of these are _required_ but I thought I wanted a section to promote other's work alongside mine.\n<p align=\"center\">\n  <a href=\"https://modrinth.com/project/4YkvO5Rp\">\n    <img src=\"https://cdn.modrinth.com/data/cached_images/5f4904d4b21ecca0de8b289c16f632f30e4a7d21.png\" alt=\"Whimscape project icon.\"/>\n  </a>\n  <a href=\"https://modrinth.com/project/NbmssBLT\">\n    <img src=\"https://cdn.modrinth.com/data/cached_images/f0c23419c3e2ae09e0dea1fd43359363a72e68ea.png\" alt=\"Whimscape x Fresh Animations project icon.\"/>\n  </a>\n  <a href=\"https://modrinth.com/project/zREUZ4Cs\">\n    <img src=\"https://cdn.modrinth.com/data/cached_images/7fedfa1314c3bfd7b85b53774e179e656bc0a6a1.png\" alt=\"Whimscape leaves project icon.\"/>\n  </a>\n  <a href=\"https://modrinth.com/project/pJnbPs9G\">\n    <img src=\"https://cdn.modrinth.com/data/cached_images/6f3d9877dd2b703c8aac8b588f28fe899fb9886b.png\" alt=\"Armor Chroma Fabric project icon.\"/>\n  </a>\n</p>\n\n> You can also [<u>**Check out my other Whimscape compatibility work!**</u>](https://modrinth.com/collection/U9BXDFq6)\n<p align=center>\n  <a href=\"https://modrinth.com/project/tn2FYfoc\">\n    <img src=\"https://cdn.modrinth.com/data/cached_images/a7121f1d69b483501f467e93a3316e6a8d32fb2b.png\" alt=\"Whimscape x Armor Chroma - Classic project icon.\"/>\n  </a>\n  <a href=\"https://modrinth.com/project/WXF8SVGX\">\n    <img src=\"https://cdn.modrinth.com/data/cached_images/e3aab31a24dca0b34a9d7b6dbfa0794e01927247.png\" alt=\"Whimscape x Chest Search Bar project icon.\"/>\n  </a>\n</p>\n\n## Author's Note\n> I found out how to change the icon texture of an empty armor slot! I think they match nicely with the rest of the resource pack.\n\n> Feel free to add this to your modpack as long as proper credit is given :)\n\n> If you want to use the resources, I ask that you give proper credit as well as respect the project's license!\n\n<p align=\"center\">\n  <img src=\"https://cdn.modrinth.com/data/cached_images/9a5fa00116692269cf67fc90a28e8a6c06c0a3c6.gif\" alt=\"Thank you message for passing 1000 downloads.\"/>\n</p>\n",
